\begin_layout Description
Teachers Dr.
 McMaster and Dr.
 Miller will be the lead teachers.
 There will be a teaching assistant to help.
 We will be joined by Dr.
 Burton Hable (University of Wisconsin-Madison) who will be observing (but not conducting any research).
 Dr.
 Hable is an expert in education theory.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
WiFi We will provide guest WiFi passes for all students.
 WiFi usage is free.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Behavior We expect all students to be respectful of others.
 Not everyone may come into this workshop at the same level,
 but this is normal.
 If anyone feels as though things are going too quickly or slowly,
 please speak up and we will gladly assist!
\end_layout

