Event We have engaged Mr.
 Joseph Pailo Haley to perform and speak on Sunday,
 22 March from 3:00 – 4:00pm in room 322 at the Mary Pappert School of Music.
 Mr.
 Pailo is an Ableton Certified Trainer who has worked extensively with some of the top companies in the electronic music industry in Los Angeles CA,
 Austin TX and Pittsburgh.
 Parents and guests are welcome to attend!
 Mr.
 Pailo will allow students to try out some of his gear afterwards.
 You can read more about him at:
